arché du travail;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">déterminer régulièrement les filières porteuses en potentiel de création d’emploi;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">analyser l’incidence des investissements sur l’emploi et la formation;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">créer une base de données sur l’emploi et la formation.</li></ul>		\n															<img width=\"1220\" height=\"813\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583.jpg 1220w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px\" />															\n			<h2>Quelques Partenaires</h2>		\n															<img width=\"417\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02.png 417w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px\" />															\n															<img width=\"417\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03.png 417w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px\" />															\n															<img width=\"417\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads