, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 0.875em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 800; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline-style: none; outline-width: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; transition-duration: 200ms; transition-property: color; color: rgb(224, 183, 25); display: inline-flex;\" rel=\"noopener\">Read more ></a></p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Encore plus\n					</a>\n			<h2>Que faisons nous?</h2>		\n		<header style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; position: relative; color: #181818; font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;\" data-bt-override-class=\"{&quot;bt_bb_size_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_size_extralarge&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;extralarge&quot;},&quot;bt_bb_align_&quot;:{&quot;current_class&quot;:&quot;bt_bb_align_inherit&quot;,&quot;xl&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;}}\"><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; clear: both; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.03em; font-size: 45px;\">ONEF est chargé de</h3></header> <ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">mener toute recherche ou étude dans le domaine de l’emploi et de la formation;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">collecter, centraliser, traiter, analyser et diffuser les informations sur le marché du travail;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">mettre à la disposition du public et des décideurs publics et privés les éléments de compréhension et d’orientation en matière de création d’emploi et d’amélioration de l’adéquation de la formation aux possibilités présentes et futures du marché du travail;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">déterminer régulièrement les filières porteuses en potentiel de création d’emploi;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">analyser l’incidence des investissements sur l’emploi et la formation;</li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">créer une base de données sur l’emploi et la formation.</li></ul>		\n															<img width=\"1220\" height=\"813\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583.jpg 1220w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/IMG_5583-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px\" />															\n			<h2>Quelques Partenaires</h2>		\n															<img width=\"417\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02.png 417w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-02-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px\" />															\n															<img width=\"417\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03.png 417w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03-300x300.png 300w, http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/logo-03-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px\" />															\n															<img width=\"417\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads