noopener\">Read more ></a></p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"1220\" height=\"813\" src=\"http://localhost/onefWPS/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><h3><a href=\"https://onef.ml/category/actualites/\" rel=\"category tag\" style=\"outline-style: none; outline-width: initial; transition-duration: 200ms; transition-property: opacity; display: block; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;PT Serif&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-repeat: initial !important; background-image: initial !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Actualités</a></h3><p><h5 style=\"margin-bottom: 0.5em; background-repeat: no-repeat; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; clear: both; line-height: 1.3em; letter-spacing: -0.03em; font-size: 1.5625em; z-index: 10; position: relative; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; max-height: 2.6em; color: rgb(24, 24, 24); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-align: left; white-space: normal;\"><a href=\"https://onef.ml/presentation-des-voeux-de-nouvel-an-2021-a-lonef/\" title=\"Présentation des vœux de nouvel an (2021) à l’ONEF.\" style=\"outline-style: none; outline-width: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; transition-duration: 200ms; transition-property: color; color: rgb(224, 183, 25); display: inline-block;\">Présentation des vœux de nouvel an (2021) à l’ONEF.</a></h5><a href=\"https://onef.ml/presentation-des-voeux-de-nouvel-an-2021-a-lonef/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, Arial